nodes.text: Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi — Ulic Qel-Droma and the Beast Wars of Onderon
Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi — Ulic Qel-Droma and the Beast Wars of Onderon was the first story-arc in the Tales of the Jedi comics series.
HighBridge Audio released an audio adaptation of the comic.
